 En general, 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\e\left(\Phi|p=p_{0}\right)=\e_{p_{0}}\left(\ind\left(T\leq k\right)\right)=\pr_{p_{0}}\left(T\leq k\right)=\pr\left(Bi\left(n,p_{0}\right)\leq k\right)
\]

\end_inset

