 Luego, 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\alpha=\sup_{p_{0}\in\left[0.1,1\right]}\e_{p_{0}}\left(\Phi\right)=\pr_{0.1}\left(T\leq2\right)=\sum_{i=0}^{2}{15 \choose i}0.1^{i}\ 0.9^{15-i}\approx0.8159
